day three of learning python today i learned conditionals of the language python (if, elif(else if), else )
i made a program that used to find largest number :


#sc

num1 = float(input("enter a number: "))
num2 = float(input("enter second number: "))
num3 = float(input("enter third number: "))

if num1 >= num2 and num2 >= num3:
  largest = num1
elif num2 >= num1 and num1 >= num3:
  largest = num2
else:
  largest = num3
  print("the largest number is:",largest)
